PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2001-21812001-11-270,  ,  ,  ,  HERITAGE
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JOHANNE BOUCHARD, of Saint-Hubert, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 19, 2001, in the place of José Faubert, whose term will expire.

precis:
